long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing B2B Rocket: AI-Powered Sales Tools Chrome Extension

B2B Rocket, the AI-driven sales tool available as a Chrome extension, is your launchpad to success. Say goodbye to traditional methods and welcome a new era of sales innovation.

Features Overview:

Quick Pricing Calculation: Easily estimate the pricing based on the number of months you wish to utilize the tool.
Package Display: Choose from our three comprehensive packages - Starter, Growth, and Scale - each tailored to meet your specific needs.
Detailed Package Information: Get insights into the features included in each package, such as the number of Agents, New Leads Monthly, Total Emails Monthly, and the option to boost with Extra Agents.

Contact us: 
- HQ: Beverly Hills, CA
- Contact: support@b2brocket.ai
